</path></svg></a>Resources</h2>\n<p>Official projects and resources of MDBootstrap.</p>\n<p>Free</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mdbootstrap.com/docs/standard/\">MDB Standard Free</a> - Free to download, open-source Bootstrap 5 UI Kit.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mdbootstrap.com/docs/angular/\">MDB Angular Free</a> - Bootstrap 5 &#x26; Angular 11 Free UI KIT with Material Design.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mdbootstrap.com/docs/react/\">MDB React Free</a> - Bootstrap 5 &#x26; React 17 Free UI KIT with Material Design.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mdbootstrap.com/docs/vue/\">MDB Vue Free</a> - Bootstrap 5 &#x26; Vue 3 Free UI KIT with Material Design.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Pro</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mdbootstrap.com/docs/standard/pro/\">MDB Standard Pro</a> - Premium UI Kit for the latest Bootstrap 5. Lifetime usage of 5000+ premium components, thousands of templates, plugins, design blocks.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mdbootstrap.com/docs/angular/pro/\">MDB Angular Pro</a> - Material Design for Bootstrap 5 with Angular.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mdbootstrap.com/docs/react/pro/\">MDB React Pro</a> - Material Design for Bootstrap 5 with React.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mdbootstrap.com/docs/vue/pro/\">MDB Vue Pro</a> - Material Design for Bootstrap 5 with Vue.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"community\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#community\" aria-label=\"community permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Community</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Projects created with MDBootstrap.</li>\n</ul>\n